type: software
title: "rijksmuseum-mcp+"
abstract: >
  An MCP server providing AI-mediated access to the Rijksmuseum collection
  via its Linked Open Data APIs, supporting search, iconographic exploration,
  high-resolution image viewing, and bibliographic retrieval.
